 light on the earth.” And it was so. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"God made the two great lights —the greater light to rule over the day and the lesser light to rule over the night —as well as the stars. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 4:19","book":"Deu","chapter":4,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 136:7–9","book":"Psa","chapter":136,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 40:26","book":"Isa","chapter":40,"verse":26,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 4:19","book":"Deu","chapter":4,"verse":19},{"label":"Ps 136:7–9","book":"Psa","chapter":136,"verse":7},{"label":"Is 40:26","book":"Isa","chapter":40,"verse":26}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"God placed them in the expanse of the sky to provide light on the earth, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"to rule the day and the night, and to separate light from darkness. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 31:35","book":"Jer","chapter":31,"verse":35,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" And God saw that it was good. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 31:35","book":"Jer","chapter":31,"verse":35}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Evening came and then morning: the fourth day."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then God said, “Let the water swarm with "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit with swarms of"},{"kind":"text","text":" living creatures, and let birds fly above the earth across the expanse of the sky.” "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit with swarms of"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So God created the large sea-creatures and every living creature that moves and swarms in the water, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 104:25–28","book":"Psa","chapter":104,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" according to their kinds. He also created every winged creature according to its kind. And God saw that it was good. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 104:25–28","book":"Psa","chapter":104,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"God blessed them: “Be fruitful, multiply, and fill the waters of the seas, and let the birds multiply on the earth.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 8:17","book":"Gen","chapter":8,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 9:1","book":"Gen","chapter":9,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 8:17","book":"Gen","chapter":8,"verse":17},{"label":"Gn 9:1","book":"Gen","chapter":9,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Evening came and then morning: the fifth day."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then God said, “Let the earth produce living creatures according to their kinds: livestock, creatures that crawl, and the wildlife of the earth according to their kinds.” And it was so. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So God made the wildlife of the earth according to their kinds, the livestock according to their kinds, and all the creatures that crawl on the ground according to their kinds. And God saw that it was good."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then God said, “Let us "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 3:22","book":"Gen","chapter":3,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 11:7","book":"Gen","chapter":11,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" make man "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or human beings; Hb ‘adam, also in v. 27"},{"kind":"text","text":" in "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or as"},{"kind":"text","text":" our image, according to our likeness. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 5:1","book":"Gen","chapter":5,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 5:3","book":"Gen","chapter":5,"verse":3,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 9:6","book":"Gen","chapter":9,"verse":6,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:29","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":29,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 11:7","book":"1Co","chapter":11,"verse":7,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:49","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":49,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 3:18","book":"2Co","chapter":3,"verse":18,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 4:4","book":"2Co","chapter":4,"verse":4,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:24","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":24,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 1:15","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":15,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 3:9","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":9,"letter":"m"},{"kind":"text","text":" They will rule the fish of the sea, the birds of the sky, the livestock, the whole earth, and the creatures that crawl "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Or scurry"},{"kind":"text","text":" on the earth.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 9:2","book":"Gen","chapter":9,"verse":2,"letter":"n"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 8:6–8","book":"Psa","chapter":8,"verse":6,"letter":"o"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 3:7","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":7,"letter":"p"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 3:22","book":"Gen","chapter":3,"verse":22},{"label":"Gn 11:7","book":"Gen","chapter":11,"verse":7},{"label":"Gn 5:1","book":"Gen","chapter":5,"verse":1},{"label":"Gn 5:3","book":"Gen","chapter":5,"verse":3},{"label":"Gn 9:6","book":"Gen","chapter":9,"verse":6},{"label":"Rm 8:29","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":29},{"label":"1Co 11:7","book":"1Co","chapter":11,"verse":7},{"label":"1Co 15:49","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":49},{"label":"2Co 3:18","book":"2Co","chapter":3,"verse":18},{"label":"2Co 4:4","book":"2Co","chapter":4,"verse":4},{"label":"Eph 4:24","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":24},{"label":"Col 1:15","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":15},{"label":"Jms 3:9","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":9},{"label":"Gn 9:2","book":"Gen","chapter":9,"verse":2},{"label":"Ps 8:6–8","book":"Psa","chapter":8,"verse":6},{"label":"Jms 3:7","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or human beings; Hb ‘adam, also in v. 27"},{"marker":2,"text":"Or as"},{"marker":3,"text":"Or scurry"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So God created man in his own image;"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"God blessed them, and God said to them, “Be fruitful, multiply, fill the earth, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 9:1","book":"Gen","chapter":9,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 9:7","book":"Gen","chapter":9,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and subdue it. Rule the fish of the sea, the birds of the sky, and every creature that crawls on the earth.” "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 9:1","book":"Gen","chapter":9,"verse":1},{"label":"Gn 9:7","book":"Gen","chapter":9,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"God also said, “Look, I have given you every seed-bearing plant on the surface of the entire earth and every tree whose fruit contains seed. This will be food for you, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 9:3","book":"Gen","chapter":9,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 104:14–15","book":"Psa","chapter":104,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 136:25","book":"Psa","chapter":136,"verse":25,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 145:15–16","book":"Psa","chapter":145,"verse":15,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 9:3","book":"Gen","chapter":9,"verse":3},{"label":"Ps 104:14–15","book":"Psa","chapter":104,"verse":14},{"label":"Ps 136:25","book":"Psa","chapter":136,"verse":25},{"label":"Ps 145:15–16","book":"Psa","chapter":145,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"for all the wildlife of the earth, for every bird of the sky, and for every creature that crawls on the earth —everything having the breath of life in it —I have given "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"I have given added for clarity"},{"kind":"text","text":" every green plant for food.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 147:9","book":"Psa","chapter":147,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" And it was so. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 147:9","book":"Psa","chapter":147,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"I have given added for clarity"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:1:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"God saw all that he had made, and it was very good indeed. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 4:4","book":"1Ti","chapter":4,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Evening came and then morning: the sixth day."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Tm 4:4","book":"1Ti","chapter":4,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783280289920}